Module jdk.management.jfr

Defines the Management Interface for JDK Flight Recorder.
Module Graph:
Since:
9

      Exports 
      Package Description
      jdk.management.jfr
      This package contains classes to control and monitor Flight Recorder over Java Management Extensions (JMX).
